I certify that the work I will be selling is my own original work, and not AI generated, drop-shipped, or stolen. If you are using a pattern created by someone else, please provide a link with proof in the additional comments that shows you have received explicit permission to use the pattern for commercial purposes.

If found to be false, your application will be withdrawn and rejected. A ban from all future events will be issued.

(Note: 3rd party manufacturing is permitted as long as it is still your original design/artwork)

I certify that the work I will be selling abides by the most recent Health Canada guidelines. It is the seller's responsibility to ensure their products remain up to date and in full compliance with all applicable regulations.

I understand that if I do not abide by these guidelines then I risk being rejected and/or removed from the event.

Useful Links:  
(consumer products) https://www.canada.ca/en/health-canada/services/consumer-product-safety/reports-publications/industry-professionals/canada-consumer-product-safety-act-guide.html

If applicable, please attach proof of membership (payment receipt, etc)

If you DMed @ubcani, an approval message from them will be sufficient.
I understand that no-shows without notice will not receive a refund, and no-shows without notice and without justification may be banned from participation in future events.
